descriptionNullable:
This Dataset Contains 4 Fish Species and thier annoted .xml files. This could be used for object detection.
The Species are : 
- Catla
- Silver
- Gulfaam
- Grass
The Dataset was annoted based on the classes

The Images Annotated here are from the following dataset : [Dataset Source](https://www.researchgate.net/publication/336268961_Fish-Pak_Fish_Species_Dataset_from_Pakistan_for_Visual_Features_Based_Classification)
